trans-unit.source: Defines a point associated with a set of workflow status events that are tracked in the potential execution path of a root workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Definerer et punkt som er knyttet til et sett med arbeidsflyten Statushendelser som spores i potensielle kjøring av banen til en arbeidsflytforekomst som roten.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] Whenever the status of the workflow instance changes, the workflow instance emits a workflow status event based on one of the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent> values to the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Når statusen til arbeidsflytforekomsten endres, arbeidsflytforekomsten avgir en arbeidsflyt status hendelse basert på ett av de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent>verdier kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent>

trans-unit.source: A WorkflowTrackPoint defines an interest in all the points during the execution of a workflow instance at which specific types of workflow status events occur.
trans-unit.target: En WorkflowTrackPoint definerer interessert i alle punktene under kjøring av en arbeidsflytforekomst som spesifikk arbeidsflyt status hendelsene oppstår.

trans-unit.source: You can add a WorkflowTrackPoint to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile.WorkflowTrackPoints%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to instruct the runtime tracking infrastructure to send a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord> to the tracking service when a specified set of workflow status events occur.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til en WorkflowTrackPoint til <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile.WorkflowTrackPoints%2A?displayProperty=fullName>til be runtime sporing-infrastruktur for å sende en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord>til Sporingstjenesten når det oppstår et angitt sett med hendelser for arbeidsflyten status.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile.WorkflowTrackPoints%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A WorkflowTrackPoint may be matched at multiple points in the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: En WorkflowTrackPoint kan samsvare på flere steder i arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Set <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint.MatchingLocation%2A> with an appropriately configured <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingLocation> to specify the types of workflow status events that the runtime tracking infrastructure uses to match the WorkflowTrackPoint.
trans-unit.target: Angi <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint.MatchingLocation%2A>med en riktig konfigurert <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingLocation>til å angi hendelsestypene arbeidsflyten statusen med kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur som samsvarer med WorkflowTrackPoint.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingLocation> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint.MatchingLocation%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can add to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint.Annotations%2A> to specify additional information associated with the track point that should be sent by the runtime tracking infrastructure when the track point is matched.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint.Annotations%2A>til å angi tilleggsinformasjon som er knyttet til spor punktet som skal sendes av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur når spor punktet samsvarer.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint.Annotations%2A>

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> is initialized with no annotations and no <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint.MatchingLocation%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>Er initialisert med noen merknader og ingen <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint.MatchingLocation%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint.MatchingLocation%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: You must set a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint.MatchingLocation%2A> for the track point.
trans-unit.target: Du må angi en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint.MatchingLocation%2A>for spor punktet.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint.MatchingLocation%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of annotations associated with the track point.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av merknader som er knyttet til spor punktet.

trans-unit.source: You can add to Annotations to specify annotations to be returned in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord> sent to the tracking service when the track point is matched.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til merknader for å angi merknader som skal returneres i den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord>sendes til Sporingstjenesten når spor punktet sammenlignet.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord>

trans-unit.source: Annotations are strings that you define that contain information to associate with the track point.
trans-unit.target: Kommentarer er strenger som du definerer som inneholder informasjon for å knytte til spor punktet.

trans-unit.source: For example, an annotation could contain information about the possible execution path the workflow can take from this track point, or it could contain information to be displayed in a user interface.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel en merknad kan inneholde informasjon om mulige kjøring-banen arbeidsflyten kan ta fra spor nå, eller den kan inneholde informasjonen som skal vises i et brukergrensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref> that contains the annotations associated with the track point.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"> </xref> som inneholder merknader knyttet til spor punktet.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty collection; it specifies that no annotations are to be associated with the track point.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er en tom samling; den angir at noen merknader som skal knyttes til spor punktet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingLocation"></xref> that specifies the workflow status events that should be matched by the runtime tracking infrastructure for the track point.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingLocation"> </xref> som angir arbeidsflyten statusen hendelsene som skal sammenlignes av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur for å spore datapunktet.

trans-unit.source: You must set a MatchingLocation for the track point.
trans-unit.target: Du må angi en MatchingLocation for spor punktet.

trans-unit.source: The MatchingLocation specifies one or more <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent> values that are used by the runtime tracking infrastructure to match the track point.
trans-unit.target: MatchingLocation angir én eller flere <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent>verdiene som brukes av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur som samsvarer med spor punktet.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingLocation"></xref> that specified the workflow status events that should be matched by the runtime tracking infrastructure for the track point.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingLocation"> </xref> som angitt arbeidsflyten statusen hendelsene som skal sammenlignes av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur for å spore datapunktet.
